<p id="fs-idp84456096">The bicarbonate ion can also act as an acid. It ionizes and forms hydronium ions and carbonate ions in even smaller quantities.</p>

<div data-type="equation" id="fs-idm146392784"><math display="block"><semantics><mrow><mtable columnalign="left"><mtr><mtd><mtext>Second ionization:</mtext></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><msub><mtext>HCO</mtext><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>q</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mtext>O</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>l</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">⇌</mo><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mtext>O</mtext><mtext>+</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>q</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><msub><mtext>CO</mtext><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mrow/><mrow><mn>2−</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>q</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mspace width="5em"/><msub><mi>K</mi><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>HCO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mfrac><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mtext>O</mtext><mtext>+</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>CO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mrow/><mrow><mn>2−</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>HCO</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></mfrac><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>=</mo><mn>4.7</mn><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo>×</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow><mn>−11</mn></mrow></msup></mtd></mtr></mtable></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mtable columnalign="left"><mtr><mtd><mtext>Second ionization:</mtext></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><msub><mtext>HCO</mtext><mn>3</mn></msub><msup><mrow/><mtext>−</mtext></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>q</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mtext>O</